    "Other accounts use these key packages to invite you into MLS groups. \"Synced\" means the package is also visible on your account outbox relays; \"Local only\" means this device has it but the relays didn't return it just now (it may not be replicated, or the relays didn't respond)." : {
      "comment" : "Footer for the list of key packages.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Other accounts use these key packages to invite you into MLS groups. \"Synced\" means the package is also visible on your account outbox relays; \"Local only\" means this device has it but the relays didn't return it just now (it may not be replicated, or the relays didn't respond)."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
